- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a relevant category as transfer entropy is a measure of information flow.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as transfer entropy has been used in machine learning applications.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses the behavior of physical quantities defined along paths, which is relevant to systems and control theory.
